{"sn2.4:0.1":"Samyutta Nikaya 2.4 ","sn2.4:0.2":"1. Pathamavagga ","sn2.4:0.3":"Magadhasutta ","sn2.4:1.1":"Savatthinidanam. ","sn2.4:1.2":"Ekamantam thito kho magadho devaputto bhagavantam gathaya ajjhabhasi: ","sn2.4:2.1":"“Kati lokasmim pajjota, ","sn2.4:2.2":"yehi loko pakasati; ","sn2.4:2.3":"Bhavantam putthumagamma, ","sn2.4:2.4":"katham janemu tam mayan”ti. ","sn2.4:3.1":"“Cattaro loke pajjota, ","sn2.4:3.2":"pancamettha na vijjati; ","sn2.4:3.3":"Diva tapati adicco, ","sn2.4:3.4":"rattimabhati candima. ","sn2.4:4.1":"Atha aggi divarattim, ","sn2.4:4.2":"tattha tattha pakasati; ","sn2.4:4.3":"Sambuddho tapatam settho, ","sn2.4:4.4":"esa abha anuttara”ti. "}